    <div class="content-box" style="background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="color: var(--accent-blue); margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fa fa-shield-alt"></i> Our Mission</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Hidden Line is built with a single philosophy: <strong>freedom of information without compromise</strong>. 
            We provide a robust, meticulously verified directory of Tor `.onion` services. We don't track you, we don't censor content, and we provide raw, unfiltered access to the Tor network.
        </p>

        <h2 style="color: var(--accent-green); margin-bottom: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-top: 1.5rem;"><i class="fa fa-bolt"></i> Core Features</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <div style="padding: 1rem; background: #0d1117; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa fa-server" style="color: var(--accent-blue);"></i> Uptime Monitoring</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4;">We regularly check `.onion` links to ensure they are live. Unlike open web links, Tor nodes drop frequently. Our automated cron system checks uptime status to save you time before you visit.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="padding: 1rem; background: #0d1117; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
