                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4;">Hidden Line uses a custom-built, Tor-proxied crawler to actively discover and index new `.onion` links, ensuring our directory remains the most comprehensive and up-to-date repository.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="padding: 1rem; background: #0d1117; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
