                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4;">True to the darknet core, all premium ad placements and services on Hidden Line are powered exclusively through automated Bitcoin gateway integrations, ensuring full financial privacy.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="padding: 1rem; background: #0d1117; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
