                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4;">Our interface is purposely lightweight. We avoid heavy JavaScript and bulky assets, minimizing network ping and ensuring maximum speed when routing through multiple Tor relays.</p>
